OL,3,CPolice failed to appreciate 'risk'
OL,4,Cbefore asylum hotel riot
OL,6,FPolice should have been better
OL,7,Fprepared for the riot outside a hotel
OL,8,Fhousing asylum seekers in Rotherham
OL,9,Fafter a protest at the same venue a
OL,10,Fyear earlier, a watchdog has said.
OL,12,FA far right mob laid siege to the
OL,13,FHoliday Inn Express in Manvers on 4
OL,14,FAugust, starting fires and throwing
OL,15,Fmissiles at police officers, who were
OL,16,Fforced to retreat.
OL,18,FThose staying at the hotel and staff
OL,19,Fhad to barricade themselves in amid
OL,20,Ffear for their lives.
