OL,6,FMore than 50 officers were injured,
OL,7,Falong with dogs and horses.
OL,9,FIt happened 18 months after two people
OL,10,Fwere arrested when anti-immigration
OL,11,Fgroups held a protest outside the same
OL,12,Fhotel.
OL,14,FHis Majesty's Inspectorate of
OL,15,FConstabulary and Fire and Rescue
OL,16,FServices (HMICFRS) has now examined
OL,17,Fhow police responded to the riots in
OL,18,FRotherham and elsewhere, which were
OL,19,Fsparked by the murders of three girls
OL,20,Fin Southport.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
