OL,6,FIn its report on Wednesday, it said
OL,7,Fprevious incidents, like the 2023
OL,8,Fprotest in Rotherham, should have
OL,9,F"influenced" the police's assessment
OL,10,Fof "threat and risk" this summer.
OL,12,FThe report said: "Our assessment of
OL,13,Fthese incidents suggests that the
OL,14,Frisks of disorder were greater than
OL,15,Fthe police believed them to be.
