OL,3,CPolice failed to appreciate 'risk'
OL,4,Cbefore asylum hotel riot
OL,6,F"They involved extreme nationalist
OL,7,Fsentiment, aggravated activism or
OL,8,Fserious disorder. All of them took
OL,9,Fplace before the Southport killings
OL,10,Fand subsequent outbreaks of widespread
OL,11,Fdisorder across the UK."
OL,13,FThe disorder in August saw trouble
OL,14,Fflare as hundreds of people gathered
OL,15,Foutside the hotel.
OL,17,FSouth Yorkshire Police sustained more
OL,18,Finjuries than any other force affected
OL,19,Fby rioting other than Merseyside
OL,20,FPolice in Southport.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
