OL,3,CPolice failed to appreciate 'risk'
OL,4,Cbefore asylum hotel riot
OL,6,FIt said: "A line of officers with
OL,7,Fshields were protecting hotel
OL,8,Fresidents and staff, who would be at
OL,9,Fsevere risk if they withdrew. The
OL,10,Fofficers had to endure sustained
OL,11,Fattack while waiting to receive mutual
OL,12,Faid.
OL,14,F"The limited number of officers in
OL,15,Fattendance amounted to a 'thin blue
OL,16,Fline' and meant dynamic dispersal
OL,17,Ftactics weren't immediately available
OL,18,Fto commanders."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
