OL,6,FSouth Yorkshire Police said it would
OL,7,Freview the report's recommendations
OL,8,F"to inform and improve our future
OL,9,Fpolicing".
OL,11,FIn a statement it added: "Alongside
OL,12,Fthis, we are currently undertaking an
OL,13,Finternal force review of all areas of
OL,14,Four police response to the violent
OL,15,Fdisorder.
